BO_ 616 frmCabinAirStateMsg: 2 BCM
 SG_ CabinTemp        : 0|8@1+ (1,0) [0|100] "degC" BCM
 SG_ AirQualityIndex  : 8|8@1+ (1,0) [0|255] "" BCM

BO_ 617 frmBodyHealthMsg: 2 BCM
 SG_ BodyAliveCnt     : 0|8@1+ (1,0) [0|255] "" VAL_SCENARIO_CTRL,CGW
 SG_ BodyDiagState    : 8|4@1+ (1,0) [0|15] "" VAL_SCENARIO_CTRL,CGW
