 SG_ BlowerLevel      : 8|4@1+ (1,0) [0|15] "" BCM
 SG_ AcCompressorOn   : 12|1@1+ (1,0) [0|1] "" BCM
 SG_ Reserved0        : 13|3@1+ (1,0) [0|0] "" Vector__XXX

BO_ 619 frmHvacActuatorMsg: 2 DATC
