 SG_ SeatVentLevel    : 12|4@1+ (1,0) [0|15] "" BCM

BO_ 623 frmDoorControlMsg: 1 BCM
 SG_ DoorControlCmd   : 0|3@1+ (1,0) [0|7] "" BCM
 SG_ ChildLockCmd     : 3|1@1+ (1,0) [0|1] "" BCM
