BO_ 626 frmBcmDiagReqMsg: 3 BCM
 SG_ BcmDiagServiceId : 0|8@1+ (1,0) [0|255] "" BCM
 SG_ BcmDiagDidHigh   : 8|8@1+ (1,0) [0|255] "" BCM
 SG_ BcmDiagDidLow    : 16|8@1+ (1,0) [0|255] "" BCM

BO_ 627 frmBcmDiagResMsg: 3 BCM
